{"tid":234157,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"醉漢擸刀 闖夜總會搵老婆","createTime":"2017-05-08T05:26:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-08T07:50:05.000Z","uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8bfa3ff8152cea478625e3b7ff058efe56ade012","tid":234157,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T05:26:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/sy/ny/api/res/1.2/OggT0CRvH1cUJI9xXiZ2Ww--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9NjY4/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/be232213f0fec096fac430f7851c5d22\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2Fsy%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FOggT0CRvH1cUJI9xXiZ2Ww--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NTQwO2g9NjY4%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fbe232213f0fec096fac430f7851c5d22&h=36d58b5a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n闖夜總會搵老婆，持刀醉漢被捕！一名姓蕭（四十四歲）男子，昨晨零時許，手持一把菜刀，闖入旺角彌敦道六○一號新興大廈一間夜總會，大聲叫嚷，又指「老婆嚟呢度搵工」。男子懷疑妻子在夜總會工作，故到上址「搵老婆」，職員見其持刀都不敢妄動，暗中報警。<br />\n<br />\n警員接報持盾牌警棍登樓搜捕，於電梯大堂發現蕭，數名警員上前合力將其制服，以涉嫌藏有攻擊性武器將他拘捕，案件由旺角警區刑事調查隊跟進。據悉，涉案男子滿身酒氣，並受情緒問題困擾多年，而其妻子並非上址夜總會職員。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%86%89%E6%BC%A2%E6%93%B8%E5%88%80-%E9%97%96%E5%A4%9C%E7%B8%BD%E6%9C%83%E6%90%B5%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86-003600624.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E9%2586%2589%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E6%2593%25B8%25E5%2588%2580-%25E9%2597%2596%25E5%25A4%259C%25E7%25B8%25BD%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2590%25B5%25E8%2580%2581%25E5%25A9%2586-003600624.html&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUoS5T71%2BpEKm9yZKOKwCwR4%3D&h=bceaf82b\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%86%89%E6%BC%A2%E6%93%B8%E5%88%80-%E9%97%96%E5%A4%9C%E7%B8%BD%E6%9C%83%E6%90%B5%E8%80%81%E5%A9%86-003600624.html</a>"},{"pid":"c7fda5f32a8bf8298ff032397bf8178083541f0a","tid":234157,"uid":54228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-08T07:26:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/asset